              <li><strong>GODZ (Shinjuku)</strong> — Best metal bar in Japan</li>
              <li><strong>Hokage (Osaka)</strong> — Metalhead pub, touring bands hang out here</li>
              <li><strong>Disk Union (Shibuya/Shinjuku)</strong> — Multi-floor record shops, massive metal sections</li>
              <li><strong>Tower Records Shibuya</strong> — 9 floors. The metal floor is a pilgrimage</li>
            </ul>
